                        "displayName": "Neal Richardson",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
                    },
                    "body": "open_dataset isn't (by default) trying to unify schemas, it just takes the first one it finds (which is why you see int32 as the types, I'd expect if you unified those schemas that you'd promote to float64). You could pass unify_schemas = TRUE to it and would probably get the error. ",
